parameters:
Celis, the Gale: I apologize for the wait. Here is the
crystal you requested.

Shimosu of the Unknown Night: Hahaha, as expected, you all
were the last ones!

Celis, the Gale: ...Hmm, the crucial part of this request
that cannot be ignored was negotiating the route.

Celis, the Gale: We win with negotiation and
transportation.

Shimosu of the Unknown Night: Wait a minute! I may have
threatened, but I successfully negotiated the route!

Storge of Benevolence: You're in front of the clients...
and in front of the rookie Clea, so please stop making
embarrassing gestures.
Guild Master Agonia: Here, all the crystals have arrived.

Guild Master Agonia: Regarding security, I believe we can
make use of the mercenaries gathered by Storge.

Noble Kasaro: Hoho, as expected of the Adventurer's Guild!
I will continue to support all of you from now on.
Guild Master Agonia: Thank you very much.

Noble Kasaro: Well, Clea, let me talk to you about the
dream we discussed the other day.
Noble Kasaro: Please come to my secret base.

parameters:
Captain Clevo: If it weren't for Nora and the others taking
care of us, we would all be dead.

Thief Nora: This is just a way to repay the favor for when
they took care of us back then, so you don't have to worry
about it so much!
Clea: I just helped my comrade Nora.
Mage Relm: It's only natural to help a friend in need!

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, that's why I think you shouldn't
worry too much about it.

Thief Nora: I'll come to meet everyone when they come
back!

Captain Clevo: Once I rescue my comrades, I intend to leave
this place.

Captain Clevo: I intend to embark on a journey to reflect
on myself, unable to forgive what I tried to do to you.

Captain Clevo: I'm sorry for being so selfish even though
you saved us.

Thief Nora: It's sad that we can't meet... but it's okay. I
believe that I will definitely meet Captain Clevo again.

Thief Nora: So... please don't do anything reckless,
absolutely absolutely... you mustn't die, okay...?

Captain Clevo: Ah, it seems like you're in need too. Take
this with you.

Captain Clevo: This is something I made when the Emma Thief
Brigade was formed. Those who have passed away probably
wanted you to have it.
Captain Clevo: Nora, thank you so much.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置

Captain Clevo: After hearing the story from Kasaro-san, I
intend to go to the royal palace with all of you.

Thief Nora: If the captain comes, we'll have the strength
of a hundred people!
Clea: Yes, please take care of me.

Captain Clevo: I should be the one thanking you. You saved
us when we were on the verge of death.

Captain Clevo: You all have prepared a new place for us to
stay.

Captain Clevo: That's why I'll fight for all of you, even
if it costs me my life.

Thief Nora: You must never die, even if it means risking
your life!

Captain Clevo: Don't push yourself too hard, Nora, who is
always getting into trouble. I'll rely on you.

Mage Relm: Because we're friends! This great genius will
take care of everything properly!

Captain Clevo: General Atu is the strongest man I've
admired. Will my sword be effective... Will my sword reach?

Captain Clevo: It seems like I can boast to those who have
gone ahead.

Priestess Sophia: Oh my, did you hear Nora-chan's story
earlier?

Thief Nora: That's right! Without the captain, it wouldn't
be the Emma Thief Brigade!

Captain Clevo: I understand... That's right, I have this
entrusted to me by Kasaro-san.

Captain Clevo: I never thought I would protect anyone other
than the Emma Thief Brigade, but this time I will fight
seriously for the people living in the Empire.
Thief Nora: Yes! Let's fight together!
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
